[{"layout":"zeppelin","isRunnable":true,"template":"dsrgmn3y","templateConfig":"{\"visualization\":{\"filters\":[{\"_id\":1583324064459,\"type\":\"styling\",\"enabled\":true,\"conditions\":{\"operator\":\"and\",\"conditions\":[{\"property\":\"hiddenConnection\",\"operator\":\"*\",\"value\":\"\"}]},\"component\":\"edge\",\"target\":\"edge\",\"properties\":{\"colors\":[\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)\"],\"style\":[\"dashed\"],\"legendTitle\":[\"Hidden Connection\"]}},{\"_id\":1590499315755,\"type\":\"aggregation\",\"enabled\":true,\"conditions\":{\"operator\":\"and\",\"conditions\":[]},\"component\":\"vertex\",\"target\":\"vertex\",\"properties\":{},\"aggregation\":[{\"source\":\"\",\"type\":\"average\"}]}],\"version\":4}}","isEditable":true,"name":"09 - Demo Select AI - Database Log Analyser Agent - Anon","description":null,"type":"medium","paragraphs":[{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":null,"message":["%md ","<center><h2 style='color:#0873d1'> Select AI - Database Log Analyser Agent <h2><\/center>"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966254094,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1776966254429,"results":[{"message":"<center><h2 style='color:#0873d1'> Select AI - Database Log Analyser Agent <h2><\/center>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":"Pre-Requisites - Configuring Select AI","message":["%md","","<b>Note:<\/b> Please refer to the `\"00 - Setup Select AI - Anon\"` Notebook for all pre-requisites on granting permissions to Packages, LLMs, Authentication and for Setting Up Credentials."],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776967247034,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1776967247483,"results":[{"message":"<p><b>Note:<\/b> Please refer to the <code>&quot;00 - Setup Select AI - Anon&quot;<\/code> Notebook for all pre-requisites on granting permissions to Packages, LLMs, Authentication and for Setting Up Credentials.<\/p>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":"Create a Database Log Analyser Agent","message":["%md","","This example shows how you can create an agent team using three agents-task pairs to retrieve logs, analyze them and then send out an email notification summarising the report.<\/br><\/br>","","**Create Agents**","","* Create the agent called `DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT` with the role to retrieve and process complex data.","","* Create the agent called `OPS_MANAGER_AGENT` with the role to analyze the data.","","* Create the agent called `EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT` with the role to send an email notification<\/br><\/br>","","**Create Tools**","","* Create an agent tool `LOG_FETCHER_TOOL` returns log entries after a given date. This uses a custom procedure fetch_logs.<\/br>","","* Create an agent tool `LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL` send an email notification.<\/br><\/br>","","**Create Tasks**","","You define three tasks `FETCH_LOGS_TASK`, `ANALYZE_LOGS_TASK` and `EMAIL_LOGS_REPORT_TASK` to guide the flow. ","","* The `FETCH_LOGS_TASK` calls `LOG_FETCHER_TOOL` to retrieve logs based on the request.","","* The `ANALYZE_LOGS_TASK` analyzes the fetched logs. ","","* The `EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_TASK` calls `LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL` to send an email notification.<\/br><\/br>","","**Create Agent Team**","","You create `OPS_ISSUES_SOLUTION_TEAM` team with `DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT`, `OPS_MANAGER_AGENT` and `EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT` to run sequentially."],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966211369,"interpreter":"md.medium","endTime":1776966211723,"results":[{"message":"<p>This example shows how you can create an agent team using three agents-task pairs to retrieve logs, analyze them and then send out an email notification summarising the report.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<p><strong>Create Agents<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Create the agent called <code>DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT<\/code> with the role to retrieve and process complex data.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Create the agent called <code>OPS_MANAGER_AGENT<\/code> with the role to analyze the data.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Create the agent called <code>EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT<\/code> with the role to send an email notification<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Create Tools<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Create an agent tool <code>LOG_FETCHER_TOOL<\/code> returns log entries after a given date. This uses a custom procedure fetch_logs.<\/br><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Create an agent tool <code>LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL<\/code> send an email notification.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Create Tasks<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>You define three tasks <code>FETCH_LOGS_TASK<\/code>, <code>ANALYZE_LOGS_TASK<\/code> and <code>EMAIL_LOGS_REPORT_TASK<\/code> to guide the flow.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The <code>FETCH_LOGS_TASK<\/code> calls <code>LOG_FETCHER_TOOL<\/code> to retrieve logs based on the request.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>The <code>ANALYZE_LOGS_TASK<\/code> analyzes the fetched logs.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>The <code>EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_TASK<\/code> calls <code>LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL<\/code> to send an email notification.<\/br><\/br><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Create Agent Team<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>You create <code>OPS_ISSUES_SOLUTION_TEAM<\/code> team with <code>DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT<\/code>, <code>OPS_MANAGER_AGENT<\/code> and <code>EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT<\/code> to run sequentially.<\/p>\n","type":"HTML"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":true,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":true,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Table","message":["%script","","-- Drop Table","DROP TABLE IF EXISTS DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966322552,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966324817,"results":[{"message":"\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS dropped.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Tables & Insert Records","message":["%script","","-- Create Table for Sample Data","CREATE TABLE DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS (","  log_id         NUMBER GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY,","  log_timestamp  DATE,","  log_message    VARCHAR2(4000)",");","","-- Insert Dummy Records","INSERT INTO DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS (log_timestamp, log_message) VALUES (","  TO_DATE('2025-03-22 03:15:45', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'),","  'INFO: Database Cluster: Failover completed successfully. Standby promoted to primary. Downtime duration: 33 seconds. Correlation ID: dbfailover102.'",");","","-- Insert Dummy Records","INSERT INTO DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS (log_timestamp, log_message) VALUES (","  TO_DATE('2025-03-23 08:44:10', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'),","  'INFO: Switchover Process: Synchronization restored. Performing scheduled switchover. Correlation ID: dbswitchover215.'",");","","-- Insert Dummy Records","INSERT INTO DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS (log_timestamp, log_message) VALUES (","  TO_DATE('2025-03-24 03:15:12', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'),","  'ERROR: Database Cluster: Primary database unreachable, initiating failover to standby. Correlation ID: dbfailover102.'",");","","-- Commit Records","COMMIT;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966340566,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966341057,"results":[{"message":"\nTable DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS created.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\n1 row inserted.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\n1 row inserted.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\n1 row inserted.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nCommit complete.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":"Define OCI API Credential","message":["%script","","-- Drop Credential","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD.DROP_CREDENTIAL('<enter-oci-api-credential-name>');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Credential does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Credentials for OCI API Key","BEGIN                                                                          ","\tDBMS_CLOUD.CREATE_CREDENTIAL","        (  ","\t\t    \tcredential_name => '<enter-oci-api-credential-name>',","\t\t\t \tuser_ocid \t\t=> '<enter-user-ocid>',","\t\t        tenancy_ocid    => '<enter-tenancy-ocid>',","\t\t        private_key     => '<enter-private-key-value>',","\t\t        fingerprint     => '<enter-private-key-fingerprint>'       ","        );                                                                           ","END;                                                                           ","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop AI Profile","message":["%script","","-- Drop AI Profile","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI.DROP_PROFILE('<enter-ai-profile-name>');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Profile does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966482027,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966482929,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create AI Profile","message":["%script","","-- Create AI Profile on Log Table","BEGIN                                                                          ","\tDBMS_CLOUD_AI.CREATE_PROFILE","        (                                                ","\t\t        profile_name => '<enter-ai-profile-name>'","\t\t    ,   attributes   => '{","                                        \"provider\"          : \"oci\"","\t\t                    ,   \"object_list\"       : ","                                                                [","                                                                        {\"owner\": \"<enter-schema-name>\", \"name\": \"DEMO_AGENTS_APP_LOGS\"}","                                                                ]","                                    ,   \"credential_name\"   : \"<enter-oci-api-credential-name>\"","                                    ,   \"model\"             : \"<enter-model-name-id>\"","                                    ,   \"oci_compartment_id\": \"<enter-compartment-ocid>\"","                                    ,   \"region\"            : \"<enter-region-identifier>\"","                                    ,   \"temperature\"       : 0.2","                                    ,   \"max_tokens\"        : 2048","                                    ,   \"comments\"          : \"true\"","                                    ,   \"conversation\"      : \"true\"","                                }'","        );","END;                                                                           ","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966491397,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966493170,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Agents","message":["%script","","-- Drop Agents","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_AGENT('DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Agent does not exist.');","END;","/","","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_AGENT('OPS_MANAGER_AGENT');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Agent does not exist.');","END;","/","","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_AGENT('EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Agent does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966618986,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966619616,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Agents","message":["%script","","BEGIN","","    -- Create Data Engineer Agent","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_AGENT(","        agent_name => 'DATA_ENGINEER_AGENT',","        attributes => '{\"profile_name\": \"<enter-ai-profile-name>\",","                        \"role\": \"You are a specialized data ingestion engineer with expertise in   ' ||","                        'retrieving and processing data from complex database systems.\"","        }'","    );","","    -- Create Ops Manager Agent","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_AGENT(","        agent_name => 'OPS_MANAGER_AGENT',","        attributes => '{\"profile_name\": \"<enter-ai-profile-name>\",","                        \"role\": \"You are an experienced Ops manager who excels at analyzing ' ||","                        'complex log data, diagnosing the issues.\"","         }'","    );","","    -- Create Email Log Report Agent","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_AGENT(","        agent_name => 'EMAIL_LOG_REPORT_AGENT',","        attributes => '{\"profile_name\": \"<enter-ai-profile-name>\",","                        \"role\": \"You are a specialized email writer which recieves an analysed log report ' ||","                        'which you must send to the Database Operations Team.\"","         }'","    );","","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966647334,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966648152,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"html","title":"Drop Log Fetcher Function","message":["%sql","","-- Drop Function for fecthing logs","DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS fetch_logs;"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966701581,"interpreter":"sql.medium","endTime":1776966701988,"results":[],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create PL/SQL Function to Fetch Logs","message":["%script","","-- Create a customized fetch_logs procedure","CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION fetch_logs(since_date IN DATE) RETURN CLOB AS","  ","  -- Declare variable","  l_logs CLOB;","","  BEGIN","    SELECT JSON_ARRAYAGG(log_message RETURNING CLOB)","      INTO l_logs","    FROM demo_agents_app_logs","    WHERE log_timestamp >= since_date","    ORDER BY log_timestamp;","","    RETURN l_logs;","","  EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","      RETURN 'Error fetching logs: ' || SQLERRM;","","END fetch_logs;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966752482,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966752894,"results":[{"message":"\nFunction FETCH_LOGS compiled\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Log Fetcher Tool","message":["%script","","-- Drop Log Fetcher Tool","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TOOL('LOG_FETCHER_TOOL');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Tool does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966777903,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966778345,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Log Fetcher Tool","message":["%script","","--Create Log Fetcher Tool","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_TOOL(","    tool_name => 'LOG_FETCHER_TOOL',","    attributes => '{\"instruction\": \"retrieves and returns all log messages with a LOG_TIMESTAMP greater than or equal to the input date.\",","                    \"function\": \"fetch_logs\"}'","    );","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966793214,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966793691,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":"Define SMTP Credential","message":["%script","","-- Drop Credential","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD.DROP_CREDENTIAL('<enter-smtp-credential-name>');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Credential does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":null,"message":["%script","","-- Create Credential for SMTP Credentials","BEGIN","  DBMS_CLOUD.CREATE_CREDENTIAL(","    credential_name => '<enter-smtp-credential-name>',","    username => '<enter-smtp-credential-username>',","    password => '<enter-smtp-credential-password>');","END;","/"," "],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":false,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":null,"title":"Enable ACL to Communicate with SMTP Server","message":["%script","","-- Enable ACL to communicate with SMTP Server","BEGIN","   DBMS_NETWORK_ACL_ADMIN.APPEND_HOST_ACE(","     host => '<smtp-server-region-identifier>',","     lower_port => 587,","     upper_port => 587,","     ace => xs$ace_type(privilege_list => xs$name_list('SMTP'),","                        principal_name => '<schema-name>',","                        principal_type => xs_acl.ptype_db));","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":null,"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":0,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":null,"row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":null},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Email Notification Tool","message":["%script","","-- Drop Email Notification Tool","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TOOL('LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Tool does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966870133,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966870571,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Email Notification Tool","message":["%script","","-- Create Email Notification Tool","BEGIN","  DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_TOOL(","    tool_name  => 'LOG_REPORT_EMAIL_TOOL',","    attributes => '{\"instruction\": \"This tool allows you to send an email to the DB Operations Team.\",","                    \"tool_type\": \"NOTIFICATION\",","                    \"tool_params\": {\"notification_type\" : \"EMAIL\",","                                    \"credential_name\": \"<enter-smtp-credential-name>\",","                                    \"recipient\": \"<enter-recipient-email-address>\",","                                    \"smtp_host\": \"<enter-smtp-host-name>\",","                                    \"sender\": \"<enter-approved-sender-email-address>\"","                      }","                  }'","  );","END;","/"," "],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966876516,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966877045,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Fetch Logs Task","message":["%script","","-- Drop Fetch Logs Task","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TASK('FETCH_LOGS_TASK');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Task does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966901581,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966902023,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Create Fetch Logs Task","message":["%script","","--Create Fetch Logs Task","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.CREATE_TASK(","      task_name  => 'FETCH_LOGS_TASK',","      attributes => '{\"instruction\": \"Fetch the log entries from the database based on user request: {query}.\",","                      \"tools\": [\"LOG_FETCHER_TOOL\"]","      }'","    );","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966907196,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966907727,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure successfully completed.\n\n\n---------------------------\n","type":"TEXT"}],"taskStatus":"SUCCESS","forms":"[]","status":"SUCCESS"},"sizeX":0,"hideCode":false,"width":12,"hideResult":false,"dynamicFormParams":"{}","row":0,"hasTitle":true,"hideVizConfig":false,"hideGutter":true,"relations":[],"forms":"[]"},{"col":0,"visualizationConfig":null,"hideInIFrame":false,"selectedVisualization":"raw","title":"Drop Analyse Logs Task","message":["%script","","-- Drop Analyse Logs Task","BEGIN","    DBMS_CLOUD_AI_AGENT.DROP_TASK('ANALYZE_LOGS_TASK');","EXCEPTION","    WHEN OTHERS THEN","        DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('Task does not exist.');","END;","/"],"enabled":true,"result":{"startTime":1776966936611,"interpreter":"script.medium","endTime":1776966937088,"results":[{"message":"\nPL/SQL procedure s